<div id='modalVote' class='modal hide fade'>
  <div class='modal-header'>
    <button type='button' class='close' data-dismiss='modal' aria-hidden='true'>&times;</button>
    <h3>Vote on the next set of improvements</h3>
  </div>
  <div class='modal-body' >
    <p>We love all the feedback you sent recently. To give you more power and influence over our work, let us know what you'd like us to focus on next.</p>
    <form id="voteform">
      <label class="radio">
        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios1" value="file export"/>File export, saving into different formats...
      </label>
      <label class="radio">
        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios2" value="bookmarks"/>Quick access to your previous maps, editing history...
      </label>
      <label class="radio">
        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios3" value="node power"/>Customising nodes: background colour, images, links, notes, ability to tick things off...
      </label>
      <input type="text" name="other" placeholder="...Or something else?" />
    </form>
  </div>
  <div class='modal-footer'>
    <a href='#' data-dismiss='modal' class='btn'>Close</a>
    <a href='#' data-dismiss='modal' class='btn btn-primary' id='sendVote'><i class='icon-thumbs-up'></i> Cast your vote</a>
  </div>
</div>
